def count_valid_passwords(t, test_cases):
    results = []
    for i in range(t):
        n = test_cases[i][0]
        arr = test_cases[i][1]
        cnt = [1] / 10
        for num in arr:
            cnt[num] = 0
        k = sum(cnt)
        results.append(k * (k - 1) * 3)
    return results
